熄機。"},{"pid":"32d5a2255e7126be1148631cd3eac1a6bb751f76","tid":1289010,"uid":156121,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:32:57.000Z","msg":"其實發電就係磁通量既改變(認真唔好笑)<br />\n一下有極大強電磁波掃過 你D電池啊 電線啊就會因為磁通量極速改變<br />\n所以有極大電流流過 做到短路既後果"},{"pid":"9bc92d4c06039a061b35f710286b0c02296b8bec","tid":1289010,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c0761808a168dca782c2e146190b13bf54c6e7","tid":1289010,"uid":208241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"emp有gamma ray？又冇vacuum tube點整到出來？<br />\n你話核彈就有姐<br />\n利申 triple e second year"},{"pid":"0e6d5ef06d6879a9d5b6156e2bc1c9e0d546c14e","tid":1289010,"uid":208241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a981c685ed9d6a8160395382516a41c29f32389d","tid":1289010,"uid":268797,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T02:29:54.000Z","msg":"我的理解：EMP ,全名是electro magnetic pulse。 利用電流變動產生磁場，如果有很大的電流變動就會有很大的磁場變動。 同理，如果有很大的磁場變動就會有很大的電流流經。  <br />\n<br />\n   設想一個電路包含電線，如果受強大的EMP 影響，電路突然會有很大的電流流經。使電器裝置燒毀，但一般電器有保護裝置，會自動cut 斷，所以為什麼有些設備糟受EMP 後過一段時間仍開得。亦有Faraday cage or shielding 保護免受扞擾。<br />\n    <br />\n    YouTube 上有人教整EMP gun/ grenade,原理一樣，用大電容（線卷好危險唔好玩）放電，不過距離短，只能使手機熄機。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"點解線圈危險？<br />\n仲有你current夠大，燒電話其實唔難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ea5b76525e4a2c20244be496577f745410633e","tid":1289010,"uid":23189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"「七黑」團結打倒白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284973\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284973</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zm1ytZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzm1ytZc.jpg&h=68603869&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b21a78dd475eb2147ed60109ea44cc1315e8eaf3"